				<div class="post-238 page type-page status-publish hentry">
	<div class="entry">
	    <h1>Kollman &amp; Saucier, P.A. is an AV-rated law firm, concentrating its practice in management labor and employment law.</h1>
<p>Since 1988, our attorneys have provided a broad range of legal services to our clients, with a particular devotion to labor and employment matters.  Although we are based in Baltimore, Maryland, we regularly handle engagements throughout the United States.  In addition to our labor and employment law practice, we represent our business clients in areas of civil litigation, transactional law, corporate law, benefit claims litigation, construction law, and real estate transactions.  We are a zealous group of attorneys dedicated to helping our clients solve problems.  This approach has served us well for the past 30 years.  We look forward to the next 30 years of service, growth and opportunity.</p>
